{"tid":2224355,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"運輸工被指藏鐵蓮花等受審　警被要求標示花槽位置　「我唔記得個槽字點寫」","createTime":"2020-09-30T12:20:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T12:54:08.000Z","uid":50386,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"68b18aa88182bb21d84ed42ae04e810aeacc846c","tid":2224355,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:20:31.000Z","msg":"民陣去年 12 月 8 日發起「國際人權日遊行」，一名運輸工人於灣仔遭警方截查，搜出刀、螺絲批及疑似「鐵蓮花」的鐵指環，被控管有攻擊性武器等三罪，他不認罪今於東區裁判法院受審。截查被告的警員吳家僖今供稱，被告當時神情慌張及眼神迴避，故將其截查。審訊期間裁判官劉綺雲，要求吳於圖片中標示案發附近的花槽位置，吳拿著圖片一度猶豫後表示「<span class=\"red\">對唔住，法官閣下，個槽字我唔記得點寫」</span>，裁判官看過圖片後，表示知悉他所標示的花槽位置。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%81%8B%E8%BC%B8%E5%B7%A5%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E8%97%8F%E9%90%B5%E8%93%AE%E8%8A%B1%E7%AD%89%E5%8F%97%E5%AF%A9-%E8%AD%A6%E8%A2%AB%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%A8%99%E7%A4%BA%E8%8A%B1%E6%A7%BD%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE-%E6%88%91%E5%94%94%E8%A8%98%E5%BE%97%E5%80%8B%E6%A7%BD%E5%AD%97%E9%BB%9E%E5%AF%AB/?fbclid=IwAR2It8tn-qylC_jXiFM29blTXlxL3_EVslSH249mJZco-Q4QR_MDrNYblt0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2581%258B%25E8%25BC%25B8%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%2597%258F%25E9%2590%25B5%25E8%2593%25AE%25E8%258A%25B1%25E7%25AD%2589%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25AF%25A9-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%25A8%2599%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E8%258A%25B1%25E6%25A7%25BD%25E4%25BD%258D%25E7%25BD%25AE-%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2594%2594%25E8%25A8%2598%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%25A7%25BD%25E5%25AD%2597%25E9%25BB%259E%25E5%25AF%25AB%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2It8tn-qylC_jXiFM29blTXlxL3_EVslSH249mJZco-Q4QR_MDrNYblt0&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyr%2FszHQdc4%2B4ddc640yZrNs%3D&h=11eb52b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2581%258B%25E8%25BC%25B8%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%2597%258F%25E9%2590%25B5%25E8%2593%25AE%25E8%258A%25B1%25E7%25AD%2589%25E5%258F%2597%25E5